Usage: setSdpTopGroup [-help] [-force] -group <sdpGroupName> {-location <llx> <lly> | -hierPath <hierPath>}

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-force                    # even the location is outside core, still set it.
                          # (bool, optional)
-group <sdpGroupName>     # Data path group name (string, required)
-hierPath <hierPath>      # Sdp module hierarical path (string, optional)
-location <llx> <lly>     # Location (point, optional)